  "texts": [
    "Alongside Forecasting and Valuation, the aforementioned ESG Disclosure, Measurement and Governance, and Financial Markets and Instruments round up the bottom three positions.",
    "The next natural question to evaluate was how the archetypical domains evolved across time.",
    "Figure 4 shows the absolute publication numbers, broken down by the archetypical domains, between 2008 and 2022.",
    "It was observed that 2018 appeared to be the inflexion point, beyond which research efforts grew significantly.",
    "In terms of the evolution of the absolute citation count as shown in Fig. 5, Trading and Investment had historically generated the highest interest across the years."
  ]
}